      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Résoudre dans $\\Rr$ l'équation $2^{4\\cos^2x+1}+16.2^{4\\sin^2x-3}=20$.",
        "html": "<p>Résoudre dans <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Rr\\)</span> l’équation\n<span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(2^{4\\cos^2x+1}+16.2^{4\\sin^2x-3}=20\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8200757f-89c3-47d6-97f7-8e630fc6d6b6",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $x\\in\\Rr$.\n\n$$\\begin{align*}\n2^{4\\cos^2x+1}+16.2^{4\\sin^2x-3}=20&\\Leftrightarrow2^{4\\cos^2x+1}+16.2^{1-4\\cos^2x}=20\\Leftrightarrow2^{4\\cos^2x}-10+16\\times2^{-4\\cos^2x}=0\\\\\n &\\Leftrightarrow2^{4\\cos^2x}-10+\\frac{16}{2^{4\\cos^2x}}=0\\Leftrightarrow(2^{4\\cos^2x})^2-10\\times2^{4\\cos^2x}+16=0\\\\\n &\\Leftrightarrow2^{4\\cos^2x}=2\\;\\mbox{ou}\\;2^{4\\cos^2x}=8\\Leftrightarrow4\\cos^2x=1\\;\\mbox{ou}\\;4\\cos^2x=3\\\\\n &\\Leftrightarrow\\cos x=\\frac{1}{2}\\;\\mbox{ou}\\;\\cos x=-\\frac{1}{2}\\;\\mbox{ou}\\;\\cos x=\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\;\\mbox{ou}\\;\\cos\nx=-\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\\\\n &\\Leftrightarrow x\\in\\left(\\frac{\\pi}{6}+\\frac{\\pi}{2}\\Zz\\right)\\cup\\left(\\frac{\\pi}{3}+\\frac{\\pi}{2}\\Zz\\right).\n\\end{align*}$$",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x\\in\\Rr\\)</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{align*}\n2^{4\\cos^2x+1}+16.2^{4\\sin^2x-3}=20&amp;\\Leftrightarrow2^{4\\cos^2x+1}+16.2^{1-4\\cos^2x}=20\\Leftrightarrow2^{4\\cos^2x}-10+16\\times2^{-4\\cos^2x}=0\\\\\n&amp;\\Leftrightarrow2^{4\\cos^2x}-10+\\frac{16}{2^{4\\cos^2x}}=0\\Leftrightarrow(2^{4\\cos^2x})^2-10\\times2^{4\\cos^2x}+16=0\\\\\n&amp;\\Leftrightarrow2^{4\\cos^2x}=2\\;\\mbox{ou}\\;2^{4\\cos^2x}=8\\Leftrightarrow4\\cos^2x=1\\;\\mbox{ou}\\;4\\cos^2x=3\\\\\n&amp;\\Leftrightarrow\\cos x=\\frac{1}{2}\\;\\mbox{ou}\\;\\cos\nx=-\\frac{1}{2}\\;\\mbox{ou}\\;\\cos x=\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\;\\mbox{ou}\\;\\cos\nx=-\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\\\\n&amp;\\Leftrightarrow\nx\\in\\left(\\frac{\\pi}{6}+\\frac{\\pi}{2}\\Zz\\right)\\cup\\left(\\frac{\\pi}{3}+\\frac{\\pi}{2}\\Zz\\right).\n\\end{align*}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    }
  ],
